This transmits revised IRM 2.3.86, IDRS Terminal Responses, Command Code IRPOL. Information Returns Processing Online (IRPOL) Command Code allows IDRS users to search, access, and display ACA forms - from insurance companies, employers, and ACA marketplaces - ﬁled to the IRS in accord to the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act (ACA) of 2010.
IRM 2.3.86 dated December 7, 2020, is superseded.
